# p_token Transfer (discriminant 3) happy-path execution trace.
# One decimal logical PC per line, in execution order.
#
# Captured from the Lean reference VM: flip TRACE_STEPS:=true in
# SVM/SBPF/Runner.lean, then
#   cargo test --features diff-mollusk --test diff_mollusk \
#     p_token_transfer_matches_mollusk -- --nocapture --exact 2>raw.txt
#   grep "^STEP " raw.txt | awk '{print $2}' | sed 's/pc=//' \
#     | while read h; do printf '%d\n' "0x$h"; done
# Inputs: amount=250, source balance=1000, dest balance=0 (see the test).
# 76 PCs = 75 executed CU + the terminal exit. Consumed by
# `qedlift --trace` to lift the real happy path (incl. balance debit/credit).
